Output
For each test case, print the following.
In the first line, print the number of operations $$$op$$$ ($$$0 \le op \le 2$$$) you want to perform. For each operation:
in the first line, output the value of $$$k$$$ ($$$1 \le k \le n$$$) you choose in the operation;
in the second line, output the number $$$s$$$ ($$$0 \le s \le \frac{n \cdot (n - 1)}{2}$$$) of simple paths you want to print;
in each of the following $$$s$$$ lines, print $$$k$$$ positive integers, representing the path $$$v_{i,1} \leftrightarrow v_{i,2} \leftrightarrow \ldots \leftrightarrow v_{i,k}$$$.
